Results.ReviewText: Went to stock up on my regular Nescafé coffee and noticed the new jar advertising the new double filter and wow can you taste the difference it is a really beautiful stronger and unique taste that you would always expect from Nescafé. Absolutely love the new taste. Definitely a most for all coffee lovers
Results.Title: New and punchy flavour

Results.ReviewText: This coffee has everything you could want. Flavour is good, strength is just right and the price is reasonable. Never mind all the so-called "luxury" coffees, this is the one for me. From the morning start-up cup to the relax-me cup once all the housework and cooking is done, there is nothing to compare
Results.Title: Greatest Pick-me-Up

Results.ReviewText: AFTER TRYING TO FIND A GOOD DECAF ALTERNATIVE, I WAS MOST PLEASED WITH NESCAFE DECAF, WITH WOODY HINTS AND SLIGHT NUTTY SMELL, ITS THE PERFECT ACCOMPANYMENT TO YOUR BREAKFAST WEETABIX. ALL YOU NEED IS A SPLODGE OF CREAM AND A DOLLOP O BUTTER ON YOUR TOAST. OR BUY A NESPRESO MACHINE AND ENJOY REAL COFFE.
Results.Title: SMOOTH TEXTURE

Results.ReviewText: From the moment the seal is broken, the rich, heady aroma promises the equivalent of liquid gold, heightening the senses  with the reassurance of consistent quality from the first cup to the last.  What a way to kick start and power through your day.  Nescafe original hits the mark, time and time again
Results.Title: Liquid Gold

Results.ReviewText: I enjoy Nescafe the best of all the instant coffees. I love the freshly ground smell you get when you open the packet, right through to the final drop of coffee from the cup! I also like the refill pack, as it is better value and saves packaging. It makes a lovely hot drink or a delicious iced coffee.
Results.Title: Nescafe original refill pack

Results.ReviewText: Love the refill packs, they are great value and I just have to top up my jar at home or work. The quality is just as good, and love the aroma as the pack opens. One spoon is enough to get that great smell and taste. For morning break a cup of Nescafe and an amaretto biccy has my colleagues drooling.
Results.Title: Bean enjoying it!

Results.ReviewText: I buy the refill packs most of the time (unless there is an offer on, trying to be truthful).  It is very satisfying opening the packet and filling up the jar again, and again, and again, instead of throwing out jar after jat needlessly.  Whether in a jar or a packet teh coffee always tastes great.
Results.Title: Great for the environment and tasty too

Results.ReviewText: This is the coffee that we always go back to.  What I mean is, there are always new instant coffees appearing on the supermarket shelves.  Well, you just have to try them, don't you?  Anyway, after trying the new coffee and finishing the jar, we go back to our trusty old favourite Nescafe Original!
Results.Title: Nescafe the Original and the Best

Results.ReviewText: I have been a drinker of Nescafe all my adult life and I am in my sixties now. Many different brands have come and go since then but Nescafe Original has always been a leader in it's field.  Even better now that it comes in refill packs as it not only saves money but is kinder on the environment.
Results.Title: Consistently good.

Results.ReviewText: For more than 15 years I drink the same Nescafe, always the original. What impress me, is the fact that I can buy it where ever I am in the world. I drink this for many years, greek style with ice in the summer, and frothy every morning, a rich flavour that none of others on the market can give!
Results.Title: P E R F E C T Taste in every cup!

Results.ReviewText: NESCAFÉ Original, in my opinon is still the best value and tasting INSTANT coffee. Over the years, I have never tasted such a relaible and satisfying coffee which gives a soothing flavour and an uncompromised beverage. Congratulations to Nescafe to keeping the value and quality over the years.
Results.Title: Original but Still Hits the Right Notes

Results.ReviewText:
Nescafé coffee has always been my only brand, and I love my coffee smooth and strong. I would prefer they went back to the brown top classic version as that was all I used to buy. Reasonable value for money and consistent quality is what Nescafé bring to the cup.
Try it with hot frothy milk.
Results.Title: Good but had better

Results.ReviewText: I love this coffee, it is rich, smooth and aromatic.  I make it with two teaspoons of coffee and just a splash of milk for my first drink of the day - it wakes me up and puts a zing in my step.  Later in the day I use less coffee and more milk for a mellower taste - it is a real hug in a mug.
Results.Title: Helps me kick start my day

Results.ReviewText:
I left the Nescafe fold to try the long list of other coffee producers who promised so much but only delivered the blandest of experiences.
Now I'm back like the prodigal son and I realise that there aint nowt wrong with the grass at this side of the fence- and never was.
Please forgive me.
Results.Title: next best thing to fresh ground

Results.ReviewText:
Rich and smooth .you cannot lose,buy a jar then refill too..You will find this coffee works for you.
Just open the jar and breathe in the smell,it makes your  tastebuds  sing'Pour on water add the milk its such a simple thing.That satisfying taste that says" Hey I am Nescafe coffee anyone?"
Results.Title: absolutely brilliant

Results.ReviewText: I buy this all the time.  I have in the past bought cheaper versions and totally regretted it. I now never look at the deals of other brands I buy Nescafe regardless of the price. Friend always comment on the taste of my coffee and I reply with 'only the best' I am officially a coffee snob!
Results.Title: NESCAFE original

Results.ReviewText: Whenever I wander away from this instant coffee, whether lured by promises of deliciousness and fulfillment, or trendy roasts and grinds, I always return to be greeted by the unforgettable smell and the unmistakeable taste of Nescafe original. Its my comfort, my familiar, my aah, Nescafe.
Results.Title: My constant, my soother!

ClientResponses.Response: Hey, thanks for the review! It saddens us to hear how unhappy you are with the changes but we're making a note of all feedback!

Results.ReviewText: I have stopped buying Nescafe Original as the flavour has become bitter since they have started to double filter it. It tastes horrid and like I say bitter. If I wanted Filtered coffee I would have a coffee maker and filter it myself. Nescafe used to be so smooth and tasty but not anymore
Results.Title: BAD choice to change

Results.ReviewText: I have always bought Nescafé original coffee, I have tried others but they have always disappointed. Not Nescafé from the time you break the seal and smell that coffee to the last spoonful in that jar it never disappoints. It's simply the best and no other coffee will enter this house !!
Results.Title: I adore this coffee

Results.ReviewText: I have tried other instant coffees over the years, but I always come back to Nescafe Original. Never disappoints, always flavourful. I use it in a number of ways, including making a really gorgeous coffe cake, and that goes wonderful with a lovely iced Nescafe coffee on a hot summers day
Results.Title: Simplly the best!

Results.ReviewText: I buy the refill because it's value for money and I love the taste of Nescafe original.  Sometimes, as a special treat, I make my coffee with just milk for a richer taste and find that Nescafe gives the smoothest flavour.  I even take it on holiday with me; I'm never without my Nescafe!
Results.Title: Good for the environment and your tastebuds

Results.ReviewText: I buy this coffee all the time as it  suits our needs i only like a weak coffee and I am able to make a coffee that is to my taste. My husband enjoys his coffee strong and he is able to make a coffee which is to his liking so all in all Nescafe Original is able to cater for every taste.
Results.Title: Universal Flavour

Results.ReviewText: This is my favourite drink to wake up to in the morning, it so full of life and vigor that it helps kick start my day.  Then when im starting to wilt and need a nice refreshing coffee it the one i go to for reviving.  I love how it makes me feel comforted but panic when i run out.....
Results.Title: How to survive the day

Results.ReviewText:
Nescafe Original is best by far, I normally drink Tea at home but when i am out at family and friends, i like to have a cup of coffee now and again
I am a veteran of the RAF and to keep me awake on a night time when i was working a 12 hr shift i use to drink Nescafe to keep me awake
Results.Title: Wonderful Taste and Aroma

Results.ReviewText: I remember the rectangular mugs and the lady in her car waiting for the sun to rise. I thought adulthood would be filled with coffee and beginnings. Coffee has moved on a lot since then and although it has lovely memories it's a little bitter for me these days. Still iconic though.
Results.Title: Makes me think of being a child

Results.ReviewText: I buy a jar off my Nescafe every week!! Yes its a weekly buy in my house! I love opening a new jar the smell is AMAZING!! I've often said the smell from the jar is enough to wake you up! Its nectar in a jar to me!! Its the real deal and nothing can substitute the smell or flavour!
Results.Title: Just the wake up needed!!

Results.ReviewText: I won't pretend that Nescafe is going to give the same experience as an individually barista-prepared coffee in a shop, but when you are at work and need something warm and comforting it does the job perfectly.  The same great taste every time, and quick so you can get back to it!
Results.Title: Just what you need when on the job

Results.ReviewText: I have bought Nescafe for years and it is a lovely smooth cup of coffee. The great thing is that it can be found just about everywhere so I can always be sure of having a quality cup of coffee when I want, wherever I am staying. No milk, no sugar, just the smooth taste of coffee.
Results.Title: Lovely smooth tasting coffee

Results.ReviewText: If you like a strong coffee without a bitter taste, this is the one, I drink it without milk or sugar and have always found it to be great value for money, this is a coffee for every day or special occasions, and it is perfect when baking because the granules dissolve completely.
Results.Title: The best by far

Results.ReviewText: So many products mess about with their formula, changing this and that and calling it "Hey - NEW amazing tasting ...". But what you want for your morning coffee is to know that it tastes as good and great as yesterday and the day before that. That's why it just has to be Nescafe!
Results.Title: Should be happy to be called "Original"

5345a1a9-0d19-4fca-aaae-bf7f6c72efdd.Description: The unmistakeable full-flavour of NESCAFÉ Original is what makes it the Nation's favourite coffee (1).
5345a1a9-0d19-4fca-aaae-bf7f6c72efdd.Name: Nescafé Original Refill

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
